<h2>HVAC mode — display or switch?</h2>
<p class="subtitle">How much control should the card expose?</p>

<div class="cards">

  <!-- Option A: Mode as label only -->
  <div class="card" data-choice="label" onclick="toggleSelect(this)">
    <div class="card-image" style="background:#1a1a2e;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:220px;gap:6px;">
      <div style="position:relative;width:150px;height:150px;">
        <svg width="150" height="150" viewBox="0 0 150 150">
          <circle cx="75" cy="75" r="56" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff12" stroke-width="13" stroke-dasharray="328 27" stroke-dashoffset="-13" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="75" cy="75" r="56" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="13" stroke-dasharray="197 158" stroke-dashoffset="-13" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;">
          <span style="font-size:9px;opacity:.4;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;">current</span>
          <span style="font-size:34px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.1">71°</span>
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:#f59e0b;">→ 72°</span>
        </div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:2px;left:2px;width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#ffffff15;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;color:#fff;">−</div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:2px;right:2px;width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#f59e0b;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;color:#000;font-weight:700;">+</div>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#f59e0b;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px;">● Heat</div>
      <div style="font-size:10px;color:#ffffff30;">Living Room</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h3>Mode label only</h3>
      <p>Shows current mode as a colored dot + text below the dial. Mode changes happen in the HA app. Simpler card.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Option B: Mode pill switcher -->
  <div class="card" data-choice="switcher" onclick="toggleSelect(this)">
    <div class="card-image" style="background:#1a1a2e;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:220px;gap:8px;">
      <div style="font-size:10px;color:#ffffff40;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;align-self:flex-start;">Living Room</div>
      <div style="position:relative;width:150px;height:150px;">
        <svg width="150" height="150" viewBox="0 0 150 150">
          <circle cx="75" cy="75" r="56" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff12" stroke-width="13" stroke-dasharray="328 27" stroke-dashoffset="-13" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="75" cy="75" r="56" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="13" stroke-dasharray="197 158" stroke-dashoffset="-13" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;">
          <span style="font-size:9px;opacity:.4;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;">current</span>
          <span style="font-size:34px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.1">71°</span>
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:#f59e0b;">→ 72°</span>
        </div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:2px;left:2px;width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#ffffff15;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;color:#fff;">−</div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:2px;right:2px;width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:#f59e0b;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;color:#000;font-weight:700;">+</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;margin-top:2px;">
        <div style="padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;background:#f59e0b;color:#000;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;">Heat</div>
        <div style="padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;background:#ffffff12;color:#ffffff60;font-size:11px;">Cool</div>
        <div style="padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;background:#ffffff12;color:#ffffff60;font-size:11px;">Auto</div>
        <div style="padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;background:#ffffff12;color:#ffffff60;font-size:11px;">Off</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h3>Mode pill switcher</h3>
      <p>Tappable Heat / Cool / Auto / Off pills below the dial. Ring color shifts with mode (amber=heat, blue=cool). Full control from the card.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
